    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aircraft designed or equipped to train pilots, general air service personnel, and flight crews in the operation of aircraft or related equipment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
